Title: In Tyr's Footsteps: The Ohn'ahran Plains
Description:
Though you have done well in your first challenge, do not think you shall surpass all so easily. Keeper Tyr meant the Engine of Innovation to be only for those worthy enough to use it wisely. 

If you are undeterred, the next challenge shall be found in the Ohn'ahran Plains. I look forward to testing your capabilities, adventurer.
ObjectivesText: Find the Second Challenge of Tyr in the Ohn'ahran Plains.
